Package org.odpi.openmetadata.adapters.connectors.governanceactions.stewardship

Enum Class WaitForStewardGuard

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<WaitForStewardGuard>
org.odpi.openmetadata.adapters.connectors.governanceactions.stewardship.WaitForStewardGuard
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<WaitForStewardGuard>, Constable
public enum WaitForStewardGuard extends Enum<WaitForStewardGuard>
The Guard enum describes some common guards that can be used when implementing governance services. Using the common guard names where possible saves time when coding the provider class and improves the ability of the service to be incorporated into governance action processes.
